    {
      "id": "695389df-f2ca-4138-b1a1-92e050422ad1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use AutoML to extract features in context of the NAEP data mining competition. In particular, 2 different packages are tested: FeatureTools and TSFRESH. ",
