    {
      "id": "6b16427a-d2a3-47c6-b576-b149ff6a7af2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thus, Bosch creates predictive models using the features extracted via the AutoML packages and compare how they perform against the features extracted from expert knowledge. The approach got 3rd on final kaggle scores and first in the public data.",
